definitions.definition: ( Internet slang , sometimes derogatory ) An extremely obsessive fan of a person, group, character, or creative work, particularly one whose fixation is unhealthy or intrusive .

main_definition: ( Internet slang , sometimes derogatory ) An extremely obsessive fan of a person, group, character, or creative work, particularly one whose fixation is unhealthy or intrusive .

definitions.definition: A country - often ex-Soviet - whose name ends with "-stan" such as Turkmenistan , Uzbekistan , and Kazakhstan .
